# ERROR TIPS

### Inventory full when harvesting
- Ensure that the agent's inventory is not full before attempting to harvest items.

### Errors when extracting from an invalid entity
- Ensure that the target entity exists and contains the item to be extracted before attempting to extract. In this case, the agent is trying to extract iron-plate from (0.0, 0.0), but there is no valid entity containing iron-plate at that location.
